quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  4,148,Mulungu sakondwera ndi kuyankhula mawu oipa pagulu kupatula kuchokera kwa amene waponderezedwa. Ndipo Mulungu ndi wakumva ndi wodziwa zonse
  4,149,"Kaya inu muonetsera pochita zabwino kapena mubisa, kapena mukhululukira zoipa, ndithudi, Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wamphamvu zonse"
  4,150,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupirira Mulungu ndi Atumwi ake ndipo afuna kusiyanitsa pakati pa Mulungu ndi Atumwi ake ponena kuti: “Ife timakhulupirira mwa ena ndipo sitikhulupirira ena.” Ndipo amafuna kusankha njira yapakati ndi pakati"
  4,151,Amenewa ndithudi ndi osakhulupirira enieni. Ndipo Ife tawakonzera anthu osakhulupirira chilango chochititsa manyazi
  4,152,"Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi Atumwi ake ndipo sasiyanitsa pakati pa aliyense wa iwo, Ife tidzawapatsa mphotho zawo ndipo Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wa chisoni chosatha"
  4,153,"Anthu otsatira a m’Buku akukufunsa iwe kuti uwatsitsire buku kuchokera kumwamba. Ndithudi iwo adafunsa Mose zazikulu kuposa zimenezi pamene iwo adati: “Tionetse Mulungu poyera.” Koma iwo anakanthidwa ndi mphenzi chifukwa cha uchimo wawo. Ndipo iwo adapembedza mwana wa ng’ombe ngakhale analandira zizindikiro zathu. Komabe Ife tidawakhululukira zimenezo. Ndipo tidampatsa Mose mphamvu zooneka"
  4,154,"Pokwaniritsa lonjezo, Ife tidakweza pamwamba pawo phiri, ndipo tidati kwa iwo: “Lowani pa chipata mogwetsa nkhope ndi modzichepetsa.” Ndipo Ife tidawalamula kuti: “Musaswe malamulo a tsiku la Sabata.” Ndipo Ife tidatenga lonjezo lokhazikika kuchokera kwa iwo"
  4,155,"Chifukwa chakuphwanya pangano lawo ndi kukana zizindikiro za Mulungu ndi kupha Atumwi popanda chilungamo ndi kulankhula kwawo koti: Mitima yathu ndi yokutidwa. Iyayi, Mulungu wamata mitima yawo chifukwa chakusakhulupirira kwawo. Ndipo iwo sakhulupirira kwenikweni koma pang’ono"
  4,156,"Ndi chifukwa cha kusakhulupirira kwawo ndi kulankhula zoipa za Maria, tchimo lalikulu"
  4,157,"Ndikulankhula kwawo koti: “Ife tidamupha Messiya, Yesu mwana wamwamuna wa Maria, Mthenga wa Mulungu,” koma iwo sadamuphe ayi ndipo sadampachike koma maonekedwe a Yesu anaikidwa pa munthu wina ndipo iwo amene amatsutsa za izo ndi okaika. Iwo sadziwa chili chonse, koma akutsatira nkhani za m’maluwa. Ndithudi iwo sadamuphe ayi"
  4,158,Koma Mulungu adamukweza kudza kwa Iye. Ndipo Mulungu ndi wa mphamvu ndi Wanzeru
  4,159,"Ndipo palibe mmodzi wa anthu a m’Buku amene angakhulupirire mwa iye, asadafe. Ndipo patsiku louka kwa akufa, iye adzakhala mboni yowatsutsa iwo"
  4,160,"Chifukwa chakulakwa kwa Ayuda, Ife tidawaletsa chakudya china chabwino chimene chidali chololedwa kwa iwo ndi chifukwa chotsekereza anthu ambiri mnjira ya Mulungu"
  4,161,"Ndi kulandira kwawo kwa katapira pamene iwo ataletsedwa kutero, ndi kudya kwawo kwa chuma cha anthu mwachinyengo. Ndipo Ife takonza chilango chowawa cha anthu osakhulupirira amene ali pakati pawo"
  4,162,"Koma iwo ozindikira kwambiri amene ali pakati pawo ndi okhulupirira amene amakhulupirira mu zimene zavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe ndi zimene zidavumbulitsidwa iwe usanadze, ndipo amapemphera nthawi zonse ndikupereka msonkho wothandiza anthu osauka ndipo ali ndi chikhulupiriro mwa Mulungu ndi tsiku lomaliza, awa ndiwo amene Ife tidzawapatsa mphotho yaikulu"